      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q">Does a roti machine work with all types of flour? <span class="icon">+</span></button>
        <div class="faq-a">Standard commercial roti machines work best with standard atta (whole wheat flour) dough. Performance varies with high-fibre multigrain flour, very coarse flours, or flours with unusual protein content. Always test with your specific flour before buying. Ask the supplier for a demonstration with your flour if possible.</div>
